"http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/9ba640a7ac7b6985c46cf498c1470596" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Nicola-Lischi-116x150.jpg" width="77" height="100" alt="Nicola Lischi" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Nicola Lischi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/nicola-lischi/">View all articles by Nicola Lischi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/10/antonio-ghislanzoni-non-di-solo-verdi/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Antonio Ghislanzoni. Non di solo Verdi&#8230;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/10/staatsoper-stuttgart-fidelio/" rel="next">Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;Fidelio&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" na